# Project-wide guidelines
Use Next.js best practices to contribute to this project.
Use functional components with TypeScript interfaces for props
Respect the existing GraphQL schema from the API
Do not update the GraphQL query and mutation
Use the path aliases defined in the Typescript configuration

# Component structure
All components should have prop validation
Place components in src/components/{ComponentName}/{ComponentName}.tsx structure
Place styled components in src/components/{ComponentName}/{ComponentName}.styles.tsx structure
Export components from an src/components/{ComponentName}/index.ts file in each component directory
All component should respect the WCAG 2.1 guidelines
Respect the Typescript interface from the existing components

# Styling guidelines
Use Emotion styled function to create styled components
Do not use Emotion css function for styling components
Do not use style object for styling components
Use the corresponding tokens from the Emotion theme to match Figma variables when appropriate
